27:13.765 --> 27:23.242 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Stay with us.

27:23.275 --> 27:28.881 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Coming up on the "NewsHour": a
high schooler
