lives.

32:16.034 --> 32:19.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they're saying something is
better than
nothing, but we will see what
actually happens

32:19.971 --> 32:21.706 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in reality.

32:21.740 --> 32:24.309 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Now, we say
unregulated. They
were unregulated by the federal
government.

32:24.342 --> 32:25.944 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: That's right.
That's right.

32:25.977 --> 32:28.280 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: But states often
were able to
regulate a lot of these
substances.

32:28.313 --> 32:30.115 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: That's right.

32:30.148 --> 32:34.252 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that was one of the final
pivot points
to making this bill become
reality, that some

32:34.286 --> 32:38.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Democrats, including Democrats
from California,
