were concerned about this.

32:42.394 --> 32:46.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they ended up carving out an
exemption
where some of the laws they
already have on

32:46.198 --> 32:51.269 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the books will stay on the
books. But, going
