32:59.344 --> 33:01.913 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: It really sounds a
little bit
to me, however, as if states are
being deprived

33:01.947 --> 33:06.518 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
