by state.

33:24.102 --> 33:28.506 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Under President Obama, those
were raised,
so that carmakers had to make
our cars more

33:28.540 --> 33:31.877 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
fuel-efficient on a national
level. Previously,
it had been on a state level.

33:31.910 --> 33:36.047 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The argument being
that a patchwork
series of law didn't apply to
