Mumbai:

34:54.592 --> 34:59.898 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ARSH SHAH DILBAGI: I felt that,
as long as
you are breathing, you should be
able to live,

34:59.931 --> 35:01.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
truly live.

35:01.733 --> 35:05.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: He's always
like to tinker,
he says. When his parents gave
him a LEGO

35:05.470 --> 35:08.306 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
