36:09.901 --> 36:15.640 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He doesn't recall the actual
light bulb moment,
when the idea popped in his
brain for a breath-driven

36:15.673 --> 36:18.476 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
