nose or mouth.

36:18.510 --> 36:24.382 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ARSH SHAH DILBAGI: The user has
to give sharp
bursts or long bursts from the
nose, which

36:24.416 --> 36:26.184 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
