36:26.217 --> 36:30.188 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: As he points
out in his
own promotional online videos,
he had to learn

36:30.221 --> 36:33.525 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
