on the idea.

36:33.558 --> 36:38.730 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ARSH SHAH DILBAGI: I had this
computation
engine which could take in
signals through

36:38.763 --> 36:44.936 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
