And it just goes in like that.

36:58.783 --> 37:04.122 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Some 35 of
them are now
being tested by users across
India. Their

37:04.155 --> 37:09.761 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
