37:14.766 --> 37:19.037 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We showed the device to Ben
Munson, a speech
scientist at the University of
Minnesota.

37:19.070 --> 37:22.807 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BENJAMIN MUNSON, University of
Minnesota:
I have high hopes for him, but
this device

37:22.841 --> 37:25.110 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
