37:37.689 --> 37:41.893 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BENJAMIN MUNSON: It's extremely
clever. He's
marketing the Wright brothers'
plane as the

37:41.926 --> 37:43.661 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Concorde or something.

37:43.695 --> 37:48.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the fact is that we live in
a day and
age where you can see in your
lifetime the

37:48.967 --> 37:52.804 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
evolution in different
technologies going
